# Placeholder so the build context always contains this directory.
#
# The Cloud Build release/dev pipelines (infrastructure/cloudbuild.release.yaml
# and infrastructure/cloudbuild.dev.yaml) build the private `heliosos`
# enterprise plugin wheel from makingscience-awake/heliosos-enterprise (using the
# HELIOSOS_ENTERPRISE_TOKEN secret in Secret Manager) and drop it here before
# the docker build. The Dockerfile builder installs any wheel found in this dir.
# When no token/wheel is present the image builds in open-source mode (the
# enterprise package is simply absent → bootstrap/urls fall back via their
# existing `except ImportError`). Actual *.whl files are gitignored.
